<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>6th Grade Math iReady Dashboard</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0f1e3c;
    --navy2: #162849;
    --teal: #0d9488;
    --teal-light: #5eead4;
    --amber: #f59e0b;
    --amber-light: #fde68a;
    --rose: #e11d48;
    --rose-light: #fecdd3;
    --violet: #7c3aed;
    --violet-light: #ddd6fe;
    --sky: #0ea5e9;
    --sky-light: #bae6fd;
    --green: #10b981;
    --green-light: #a7f3d0;
    --slate: #64748b;
    --cream: #f8f5f0;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --t1-color: #10b981;
    --t2-color: #f59e0b;
    --t3-color: #e11d48;
    --card-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(15,30,60,0.12);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--navy);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  header { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); padding: 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.35); }
  .header-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 32px; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .header-title { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .header-title h1 { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.45rem; letter-spacing: .3px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .header-title span { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--teal-light); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .8px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* COUNTDOWN */
  .countdown-box { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #be123c, #7c3aed); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 18px; }
  .cd-icon { font-size: 1.7rem; }
  .cd-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .cd-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .countdown-label { font-size: .62rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #fde68a; font-weight: 800; }
  .countdown-date { font-size: .72rem; color: #fde68a; font-weight: 600; }
  .cd-grid { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .cd-unit { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; min-width: 34px; }
  .cd-val { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #fff; line-height: 1; font-weight: 700; }
  .cd-lbl-small { font-size: .55rem; color: #e9d5ff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* NAV TABS */
  .tab-nav { display: flex; gap: 0; background: var(--navy2); padding: 0 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06); overflow-x: auto; }
  .tab-btn { background: none; border: none; color: #94a3b8; padding: 11px 22px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; transition: all .2s; white-space: nowrap; letter-spacing: .4px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--teal-light); border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }

  /* MAIN */
  main { padding: 28px 32px; max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .tab-pane { display: none; animation: fadeIn .3s ease; }
  .tab-pane.active { display: block; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  .section-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .section-sub { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 22px; }

  /* STAT CARDS */
  .stat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(168px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .stat-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 20px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .stat-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: var(--accent, var(--teal)); border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; }
  .stat-label { font-size: .7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .8px; color: var(--slate); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .stat-value { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .stat-detail { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--slate); }

  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .three-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 960px) { .two-col, .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); }
  .card-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .card-title .icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 7px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: .85rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .placement-bar-wrap { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .placement-label { font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .placement-bar-bg { background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; height: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  .placement-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; transition: width .8s ease; }

  .domain-bars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .domain-name { font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 3px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .domain-bar-bg { background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; height: 22px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .domain-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-right: 8px; font-size: .65rem; color: white; font-weight: 700; transition: width .8s; }
  .domain-bar-benchmark { position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: var(--rose); }

  .standards-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: .78rem; }
  .standards-table th { background: var(--navy); color: white; padding: 9px 12px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: .7rem; letter-spacing: .5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .standards-table td { padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; vertical-align: top; }
  .standards-table tr:hover td { background: #f8fafc; }
  .std-code { font-family: monospace; font-size: .7rem; background: #e0f2fe; color: #0369a1; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: 700; }
  .gap-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .gap-high { background: #fecdd3; color: #be123c; }
  .gap-med { background: #fde68a; color: #92400e; }
  .gap-low { background: #bbf7d0; color: #065f46; }
  .gap-crit { background: #fee2e2; color: #7f1d1d; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }

  .student-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  .student-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: .76rem; }
  .student-table th { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); padding: 9px 11px; text-align: left; font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .4px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
  .student-table td { padding: 8px 11px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; white-space: nowrap; }
  .student-table tr:hover td { background: #f8fafc; }
  .placement-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: .66rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .pt-g2 { background: #fecdd3; color: #be123c; }
  .pt-g3 { background: #ffe4e6; color: #9f1239; }
  .pt-g4 { background: #fef3c7; color: #854d0e; }
  .pt-g5 { background: #fef9c3; color: #713f12; }
  .pt-e6 { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
  .pt-m6 { background: #bbf7d0; color: #065f46; }
  .pt-l6 { background: #a7f3d0; color: #064e3b; }
  .pt-max { background: #c7d2fe; color: #1e3a8a; font-weight:800; }
  .pt-g7 { background: #c7d2fe; color: #312e81; }
  .pt-g8 { background: #ddd6fe; color: #4c1d95; }
  .pt-g9 { background: #e9d5ff; color: #581c87; }

  .tier-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .tier-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .tier-card { border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); border-top: 5px solid; }
  .tier-card.t1 { background: #f0fdf4; border-color: var(--green); }
  .tier-card.t2 { background: #fffbeb; border-color: var(--amber); }
  .tier-card.t3 { background: #fff1f2; border-color: var(--rose); }
  .tier-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tier-num { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .t1 .tier-num { background: var(--green); color: white; }
  .t2 .tier-num { background: var(--amber); color: white; }
  .t3 .tier-num { background: var(--rose); color: white; }
  .tier-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; }
  .tier-count { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 1px; }

  .tier-student-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .tier-student { background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .tier-avatar { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: .82rem; flex-shrink: 0; color: white; }
  .tier-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .tier-sname { font-weight: 700; font-size: .8rem; }
  .tier-room { font-size: .68rem; color: var(--slate); }
  .tier-gaps { margin-top: 4px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
  .gap-tag { font-size: .62rem; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; }

  .action-card { background: white; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); margin-bottom: 18px; border-left: 5px solid; }
  .action-card.t3 { border-color: var(--rose); }
  .action-card.t2 { border-color: var(--amber); }
  .action-card.t1 { border-color: var(--green); }
  .action-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .action-tier-badge { padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .4px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .t3 .action-tier-badge { background: var(--rose); color: white; }
  .t2 .action-tier-badge { background: var(--amber); color: white; }
  .t1 .action-tier-badge { background: var(--green); color: white; }
  .action-title { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.08rem; }
  .action-body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .action-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .action-section-title { font-size: .7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .7px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .action-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .action-list li { font-size: .78rem; display: flex; gap: 8px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .action-list li::before { content: '▸'; color: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .action-students { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px; }
  .student-chip { background: var(--navy); color: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 11px; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 600; }

  .student-search-wrap { margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .search-input { flex: 1; min-width: 220px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 16px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .88rem; outline: none; transition: border .2s; }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .filter-select { border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .85rem; outline: none; background: white; cursor: pointer; }
  .student-profile { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px; box-shadow: var(--card-shadow); display: none; }
  .profile-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .profile-avatar { width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: white; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .profile-name { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .profile-meta { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 4px; }
  .profile-chips { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 8px; }
  .profile-chip { padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; }

  .profile-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .profile-metric { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; text-align: center; }
  .pm-label { font-size: .65rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .7px; color: var(--slate); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pm-value { font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1; }
  .pm-sub { font-size: .68rem; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 3px; }

  .domain-profile { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .domain-profile { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .domain-pcard { background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; border-left: 4px solid; }
  .dp-title { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .6px; color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dp-placement { font-weight: 700; font-size: .88rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dp-score { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--slate); }
  .dp-std { font-size: .68rem; color: var(--slate); margin-top: 4px; font-family: monospace; }

  .standards-match { margin-top: 6px; }
  .std-match-item { font-size: .7rem; padding: 5px 0; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }

  .growth-bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .gbr-label { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; width: 140px; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--slate); }
  .gbr-bar-wrap { flex: 1; }
  .gbr-bg { background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 6px; height: 18px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .gbr-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; padding-right: 6px; font-size: .62rem; color: white; font-weight: 700; }
  .gbr-target { position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: #334155; }

  .no-selection { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--slate); font-size: .9rem; }
  .no-selection .big { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }

  .homeroom-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 22px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .hr-tab { padding: 9px 20px; background: none; border: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; color: var(--slate); border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -2px; transition: all .2s; }
  .hr-tab.active { color: var(--teal); border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }
  .hr-tab:hover { color: var(--navy); }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 3px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #94a3b8; border-radius: 3px; }

  .legend-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: .72rem; color: var(--slate); }
  .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .callout { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; border-left: 5px solid var(--amber); display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .callout-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .callout-title { font-weight: 800; font-size: .82rem; color: #78350f; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .callout-txt { font-size: .75rem; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.5; }

  @media print { header { position: static; } .tab-btn { display: none; } .tab-pane { display: block !important; page-break-after: always; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-title">
      <h1>6th Grade Math iReady Dashboard</h1>
      <span>YTD Diagnostic Analysis · Florida B.E.S.T. Standards Alignment · Source: iReady Connect</span>
    </div>
    <div class="countdown-box">
      <div class="cd-icon">⏳</div>
      <div class="cd-body">
        <div class="cd-top">
          <div class="countdown-label">FAST Math PM3</div>
          <div class="countdown-date">May 12, 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cd-grid">
          <div class="cd-unit"><div class="cd-val" id="cd-days">--</div><div class="cd-lbl-small">Days</div></div>
          <div class="cd-unit"><div class="cd-val" id="cd-hours">--</div><div class="cd-lbl-small">Hrs</div></div>
          <div class="cd-unit"><div class="cd-val" id="cd-mins">--</div><div class="cd-lbl-small">Min</div></div>
          <div class="cd-unit"><div class="cd-val" id="cd-secs">--</div><div class="cd-lbl-small">Sec</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <nav class="tab-nav">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('overview', event)">📊 Overview</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('class', event)">🏫 Class View</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('standards', event)">📋 Standards &amp; Gaps</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('individual', event)">👤 Individual</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('tiers', event)">🎯 Tier Placement</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('action', event)">📝 Action Plan</button>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>

<!-- OVERVIEW -->
<div id="tab-overview" class="tab-pane active">
  <div class="section-title">School Overview</div>
  <div class="section-sub">6th Grade Math · All Class Periods · YTD Diagnostic Results (121 students)</div>

  <div class="callout">
    <div class="callout-icon">⚠️</div>
    <div>
      <div class="callout-title">CRITICAL: iReady → FAST Math PM3 Ratios, Expressions &amp; Integer Blind Spots</div>
      <div class="callout-txt">iReady Math for 6th grade reports 4 domains: Number &amp; Operations, Algebra &amp; Algebraic Thinking, Measurement &amp; Data, Geometry. FAST Math PM3 reports five categories — Number Sense &amp; Operations (incl. integers), <strong>Algebraic Reasoning</strong> (ratios, rates, expressions, equations, inequalities), Geometric Reasoning, and Data Analysis &amp; Probability. iReady's Algebra domain blends ratios + expressions + equations into one score, masking which strand is weak. <strong>MA.6.AR.1</strong> (ratios/rates/percents) and <strong>MA.6.NSO.4</strong> (integers/absolute value) need targeted formative checks before 5/12.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stat-grid" id="overview-stats"></div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="icon" style="background:#dbeafe">📊</div> Overall Placement Distribution</div>
      <div id="placement-dist"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="icon" style="background:#d1fae5">📈</div> Growth Summary (Baseline → Latest)</div>
      <div id="growth-summary"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="icon" style="background:#fef3c7">🎯</div> Domain Performance (% On or Above Grade)</div>
      <div class="domain-bars" id="domain-overview"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="icon" style="background:#ede9fe">⚡</div> Top Growth Stars (Gain Points)</div>
      <div id="growth-stars"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CLASS VIEW -->
<div id="tab-class" class="tab-pane">
  <div class="section-title">Class View by Math Period</div>
  <div class="section-sub">Compare performance across the six 6th grade math sections (Braswell × 5 + Rutledge × 1)</div>
  <div class="homeroom-tabs" id="hr-tabs"></div>
  <div id="hr-content"></div>
</div>

<!-- STANDARDS -->
<div id="tab-standards" class="tab-pane">
  <div class="section-title">Florida B.E.S.T. Standards Alignment &amp; Gaps</div>
  <div class="section-sub">iReady Math domains mapped to Florida B.E.S.T. MA.6 standards · Red = high need · Source: iReady Connect</div>

  <div class="two-col" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
