        'Ratio tables and double number lines — daily 5-minute warm-ups with real contexts (recipes, mileage)',
        'Algebra tiles for evaluating expressions and modeling one-step equations',
        'FAST-formatted item-type exposure 2x/week: multi-select, drag-and-drop, equation editor, coordinate plane plotting',
