        'Ratio reasoning daily warm-up — tape diagrams, ratio tables, double number lines',
        'Integer operations using two-color counters and number-line "walks"',
        'Error-analysis routine: students explain WHY a wrong answer is wrong using math vocabulary',
        'Box plot construction unit — build from raw data sets, focus on quartiles and IQR',
        'iReady: maintain 45+ min/week; use teacher dashboard to monitor lesson completion',
