        'MA.6.GR.1–2 — Coordinate plane (4 quadrants), area, volume, surface area via nets',
        'MA.6.DP.1 — Statistical questions, dot plots, histograms, box plots, measures of center/spread',
        'Cross-strand connections: ratio reasoning ↔ proportional graphs ↔ unit rates'
      ],
      strategies: [
        'Whole-class rigorous Tier 1 instruction with differentiated questioning and tiered tasks',
        'Math discourse: "Talk moves" — restate, add on, agree/disagree with evidence',
